trans-unit.source: Contains the specific settings for an instance of a custom peer resolver service.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder innstillingene for spesifikke for en forekomst av en egendefinert node Løsningsprogrammet tjeneste.

trans-unit.source: This type defines the basic settings for a custom peer resolver service, including the endpoint address of the peer hosting the service and any specific binding settings.
trans-unit.target: Denne typen definerer de grunnleggende innstillingene for en egendefinert node Løsningsprogrammet tjeneste, inkludert Endepunktsadressen av node som vert for tjenesten og innstillinger spesifikk binding.

trans-unit.source: These settings are typically provided to the <xref:System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerResolverSettings.Custom%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Disse innstillingene vanligvis er angitt i <xref:System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerResolverSettings.Custom%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerResolverSettings.Custom%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerCustomResolverSettings"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerCustomResolverSettings"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the endpoint address of the peer node hosting the custom peer resolver service.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir Endepunktsadressen for node-noden vertstjeneste egendefinerte node Løsningsprogrammet.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress> that contains the endpoint address of the peer node running the custom peer resolver service.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress>som inneholder Endepunktsadressen for node-noden kjører egendefinerte node Løsningsprogrammet-tjenesten.</xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the channel binding used by the custom peer resolver service.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir kanal bindingen brukes av tjenesten egendefinerte node Løsningsprogrammet.

trans-unit.source: This binding element provides the specification for building a channel factory on the client and a channel listener on the service.
trans-unit.target: Bindingselementet gir oppsettet for å bygge en kanal til fabrikkinnstillingene på klienten og et kanallytteobjekt for tjenesten.

trans-unit.source: This channel factory is used to produce channels for the custom peer resolver service.
trans-unit.target: Denne kanalfabrikken brukes til å produsere kanaler for egendefinert node Løsningsprogrammet-tjenesten.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Binding> that contains the binding settings for this service.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Binding>som inneholder innstillingene for binding for denne tjenesten.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Binding>

trans-unit.source: Gets whether the <xref:System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerCustomResolverSettings.Binding*> property is set.
True if the <xref:System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerCustomResolverSettings.Binding*> property is set; false if it is not.
trans-unit.target: True hvis den <xref:System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerCustomResolverSettings.Binding*>egenskapen er angitt; false Hvis den ikke.</xref:System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerCustomResolverSettings.Binding*>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the custom peer resolver instance for this service.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir egendefinerte node Løsningsprogrammet forekomsten for denne tjenesten.
